quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  9,21,un ka perwar-digaar un ko apni rehmat ki aur khushnodi ki aur bahishtoon ki khushkhabri deta hai jin mein un ke liye Nemat haae javedani hai
  9,22,( aur woh ) un mein abdul aabad rahen ge. kuch shak nahi ke khuda ke haan bara sila ( tayyar ) hai
  9,23,ae ahal imaan! agar tumahray ( maa ) baap aur ( behan ) bhai imaan ke maqabil kufar ko pasand karen to un se dosti nah rakho. aur jo un se dosti rakhen ge woh zalim hain
  9,24,keh do ke agar tumahray baap aur betay aur bhai aur aurtain aur khandan ke aadmi aur maal jo tum kamate ho aur tijarat jis ke band honay se drtay ho aur makanaat jin ko pasand karte ho khuda aur is ke rasool se aur khuda ki raah mein jehaad karne se tumhe ziyada Aziz hon to thehray raho yahan taq ke khuda apna hukum ( yani azaab ) beje. aur khuda nafarman logon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  9,25,khuda ne bohat se moqaon par tum ko madad di hai aur ( jung ) Hunain ke din. jab tum ko apni ( jamaat ki ) kasrat par ghara tha to woh tumahray kuch bhi kaam nah aayi. aur zameen bawajood ( itni barri ) farakhi ke tum par tang hogayi phir tum peeth phair kar phir gay
  9,26,phir khuda ne apne paighambar par aur mominon par apni taraf se taskeen nazil farmai ( aur tumhari madad ko firshton ke ) lashkar jo tumhe nazar nahi atay they ( aasman se ) utaray aur kafiroon ko azaab diya. aur kufar karne walon ki yahi saza hai
